graph TB
    subgraph "CodeFlare Operator"
        Manager[Manager Deployment]
        MCAD[MCAD Queue Controller<br/>Embedded v1.38.1]
        InstaScale[InstaScale Controller<br/>Optional - Disabled by default]
        MetricsService[Metrics Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]

        Manager -->|hosts| MCAD
        Manager -->|hosts| InstaScale
        Manager -->|exposes| MetricsService
    end

    User[User/CodeFlare SDK] -->|creates| AppWrapperCR[AppWrapper CR<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta1]
    User -->|creates| QuotaCR[QuotaSubtree CR<br/>quota.codeflare.dev/v1alpha1]

    AppWrapperCR -->|watched by| MCAD
    QuotaCR -->|watched by| MCAD

    MCAD -->|creates| RayCluster[RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io]
    MCAD -->|creates| Pods[Pods]
    MCAD -->|creates| Jobs[Jobs]
    MCAD -->|creates| Deployments[Deployments]
    MCAD -->|creates| Routes[Routes/Ingresses<br/>Ray Dashboard]

    InstaScale -->|watches| AppWrapperCR
    InstaScale -->|scales| MachineSets[MachineSets<br/>machine.openshift.io]

    MCAD -->|depends on| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.0.0-rc.0]
    InstaScale -->|depends on| MachineAPI[OpenShift Machine API]

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics| MetricsService

    style Manager fill:#4a90e2
    style MCAD fill:#4a90e2
    style InstaScale fill:#7ed321
    style MetricsService fill:#4a90e2
    style AppWrapperCR fill:#f5a623
    style QuotaCR fill:#f5a623
    style RayCluster fill:#7ed321
    style KubeRay fill:#999
    style MachineAPI fill:#999
    style Prometheus fill:#999
